A spokesperson for Sons & Daughters said they were “shocked and depressed” by his death.
"We are a small team that works as a friendly family and will be very much lacking," the representative said.
Our thoughts and condolences to Frank’s family and friends during this difficult time.
Luis Gal<0xC3><0xAD>cia said that Frank had stayed at the hostels at first, but lately, “Finally, things are going well for him.”
“He found an apartment, he met a girl,” Luis Galisia told KGO.
Luis Gal<0xC3><0xAD>cia said he couldn’t imagine someone who wanted to hurt his younger brother.
He had a good heart and a good heart.
