Notifications for transport tax will cease to be sent by mail - website Driving www.zr.ru
The Tax Inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notifications of property taxes.
All Russian car owners are used to the unchanged scheme for years: in the summer and autumn they receive by mail a receipt for the payment of transport tax for the previous year.
However, many of them are not expected this year.
The fact is that the tax inspection without unnecessary noise has changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
For those who are registered in the "Personal Office of the taxpayer" on the official website of the nalog.ru agency, notifications will come in electronic form.
In the inspection automatically considered such Russians as online users and excluded them from the standard, "paper" mailing.
The news will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
Everyone else will still receive the usual e-mails.
However, there is an opportunity to return to the old scheme and the account holders on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax department during August and write a statement.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and comfortable.
The notification will appear in the "personal office" immediately after compilation, while the letter will last a few days and may be lost at all.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of the tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to save seriously on the mailing.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection site is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in a "personal office" for a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without knowing it themselves, will fall into the category of non-payers with all the consequences.
Access to the "Personal Account of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, by electronic signature or by entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained in person in any department of the tax inspection (regardless of the place of registration).
Please note that this year the transport tax must be paid before December 1.
The sending of notifications began in July.
